data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5K USE AS YOU CHOOSE. This 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with a separate bonus loft room & 2 car garage located in the community of Highgrove could be the one! With an open concept kitchen & living room there is lots of space to entertain showcasing beautiful upgraded flooring. The kitchen features plenty of cabinet & counter space with an eat at kitchen island & double sink. On the 1st floor there is a guest bedroom & half bath. The 2nd floor boasts the primary bedroom with ensuite providing dual vanity, walk in shower & WIC. On the 2nd floor you will also find 3 additional bedrooms & a bonus loft room, the perfect space for a toy room or movie night. Walk in laundry is also located on the 2nd floor. The back yard backs to the woodline with wonderful privacy & great yard space to transform into your own. This property is conveniently located to shopping/dining & a 20-25 minute commute to Fort Liberty. Community offers a cute pond & park for the kiddos. Come see!!
